Package: python3-i2pchat
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
 python3 (>= 3.12~),
 i2pd (>= 2.49.0),
 python3-cryptography,
 python3-keyring,
 python3-nacl,
 python3-pil,
 python3-pyperclip,
 python3-pyqt6,
 python3-qasync,
 python3-rich,
 python3-textual
Description: I2PChat shared Python runtime
 Experimental peer-to-peer chat client for the I2P anonymity network.
 .
 This package contains the shared Python modules and entry points used by the
 graphical and terminal frontends. It expects a system-provided i2pd router.
 Newer i2pd (for example 2.59+) is recommended for full feature parity with
 upstream releases.

